name: Lucky Charm Treasure (elegy and (re)percussion)
description: This NFT es part of the art project ELEGY AND  (RE)PERCUSSION, 2019-2021, ainly formed by punching 1,104 coins by hand and stamping them with the motto SÍ MEREZCO ABUNDIANCIA (I deserve affluence). So, I decided to mint this artwork as a lucky charm amulet for everyone. Book available -> https://bit.ly/3iRb56v
